      <guid>https://artbrushray.github.io/posts/sep25mix/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Mix of my recently published artworks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AdMech vs some Heretics fan art&lt;/strong&gt;
&lt;img loading=&#34;lazy&#34; src=&#34;https://artbrushray.github.io/img/2025/Mechanicus-vs-heretics-by-brushray-h.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;AdMech vs some Heretics fan art, fan art by Dmitry Brushray&#34;  /&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hey everyone!
What I love about AdMech is that if a hand or leg a bit longer than it should be, it&amp;rsquo;s not a problem it&amp;rsquo;s an AdMech thing, you know.
So yeh, scale might be a little bit off. However I wanted to paint a titan and a dunecrawler in a single battle scene. I hope you like it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
